00:06:58.440 --> 00:07:00.150 align:middle line:90%
There is no downside to that.

00:07:00.150 --> 00:07:01.260 align:middle line:90%
So he did.

00:07:01.260 --> 00:07:04.110 align:middle line:84%
And he lived much, much
longer than anyone thought.

00:07:04.110 --> 00:07:06.060 align:middle line:90%
