cancer patient has cancer.

00:07:33.240 --> 00:07:34.590 align:middle line:90%
And they live longer.

00:07:34.590 --> 00:07:38.040 align:middle line:84%
And they're able to enjoy
more months and more years.

00:07:38.040 --> 00:07:39.750 align:middle line:90%
